title: Dakine Split Roller Bag 100L/65L
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Split Roller Bag 100L and 65L in Carbon.
Split Roller Features: 
- Split level design allows for easy access
- Retractable handle
- Replaceable urethane wheels
- Exterior organizer pockets
- Lockable zipper cars
